statements: SELECT * FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data;
SELECT doctor_id, consultation_date, consultation_time FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data;
SELECT patient_id, doctor_id, consultation_date, consultation_time, duration_minutes FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE doctor_id = 102;
SELECT patient_id, consultation_date, consultation_time, consultation_notes FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE patient_id = 201;
SELECT * FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data ORDER BY consultation_date DESC, consultation_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE patient_id = 123;
SELECT consultation_id, doctor_id, consultation_date, consultation_time, duration_minutes FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE doctor_id = 456;
SELECT patient_id, doctor_id, consultation_date FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE consultation_time > '09:00:00';
SELECT consultation_id, consultation_notes FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE duration_minutes > 30 ORDER BY consultation_date DESC, consultation_time ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT doctor_id, COUNT(*) AS consultations_count FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data GROUP BY doctor_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT * FROM consultation_data WHERE consultation_id = '12345';
SELECT consultation_date, consultation_duration FROM consultation_data ORDER BY consultation_date DESC;
SELECT consultation_id, doctor_id, patient_id FROM consultation_data WHERE consultation_type = 'Telemedicine' LIMIT 10;
SELECT doctor_id, patient_id, consultation_date FROM consultation_data WHERE consultation_date > '2022-01-01' AND consultation_date < '2022-06-30';
SELECT consultation_id, AVG(performance_rating) AS avg_performance_rating FROM performance_metrics GROUP BY consultation_id HAVING AVG(performance_rating) > 3.5;
SELECT * FROM consultation_data ORDER BY consultation_date DESC, consultation_duration ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT consultation_id, consultation_type, COUNT(*) FROM consultation_data GROUP BY consultation_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT cd.consultation_id, cd.consultation_date, pm.engagement_score FROM consultation_data cd JOIN performance_metrics pm ON cd.consultation_id = pm.consultation_id WHERE pm.engagement_score > 80;
SELECT cd.doctor_id, COUNT(pm.metric_id) FROM consultation_data cd LEFT JOIN performance_metrics pm ON cd.consultation_id = pm.consultation_id GROUP BY cd.doctor_id HAVING COUNT(pm.metric_id) < 5;
SELECT * FROM consultation_data WHERE patient_id IN (SELECT patient_id FROM consultation_data GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) ORDER BY consultation_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM VirtualConsultations;
SELECT consultation_id, consultation_date, consultation_outcome FROM VirtualConsultations;
SELECT patient_id, total_consultations, satisfaction_rating FROM PatientMetrics ORDER BY patient_id DESC;
SELECT trend_name, trend_start_date, trend_end_date FROM TrendAnalysis WHERE trend_analysis_results LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT * FROM PatientMetrics WHERE last_consultation_date >= '2022-01-01' AND satisfaction_rating > 4 ORDER BY satisfaction_rating DESC, total_consultations ASC;
SELECT * FROM VirtualConsultations WHERE consultation_duration > 30 ORDER BY consultation_date DESC;
SELECT patient_id, total_consultations, average_consultation_duration FROM PatientMetrics WHERE satisfaction_rating >= 4 ORDER BY total_consultations DESC;
SELECT consultation_id, patient_id, consultation_outcome FROM VirtualConsultations JOIN PatientMetrics ON VirtualConsultations.patient_id = PatientMetrics.patient_id;
SELECT trend_id, trend_name, trend_start_date, trend_end_date FROM TrendAnalysis WHERE trend_end_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY trend_start_date;
SELECT * FROM VirtualConsultations WHERE consultation_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-01';
SELECT * FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data;
SELECT consultation_id, consultation_date, consultation_duration FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE consultation_rating > 4.0;
SELECT doctor_id, COUNT(*) AS total_consultations FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data GROUP BY doctor_id;
SELECT * FROM Improvement_Strategies WHERE strategy_status = 'In Progress';
SELECT trend_name, AVG(trend_value) AS average_value FROM Consultation_Trends GROUP BY trend_name;
SELECT * FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data ORDER BY consultation_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT consultation_id, consultation_duration FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE consultation_rating > 4;
SELECT AVG(consultation_duration) AS average_duration FROM Virtual_Consultation_Data WHERE doctor_id = '1abc-1234';
SELECT * FROM Performance_Metrics WHERE metric_value BETWEEN 100.00 AND 200.00;
SELECT trend_name, trend_value FROM Consultation_Trends WHERE trend_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM consultation_requests;
SELECT request_id, consultation_date, consultation_time FROM consultation_requests WHERE consultation_type = 'Initial Consultation';
SELECT user_id, user_name FROM consultation_users ORDER BY user_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM consultation_feedback WHERE feedback_score > 4;
SELECT analysis_type, analysis_results FROM consultation_analysis;
SELECT * FROM consultation_requests WHERE consultation_type = 'Virtual' ORDER BY consultation_date DESC, consultation_time DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT request_id, consultation_date, consultation_time, consultation_type FROM consultation_requests INNER JOIN consultation_users ON consultation_requests.user_id = consultation_users.user_id WHERE user_role = 'Consultant' AND consultation_duration > 60 ORDER BY consultation_date ASC;
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_score, feedback_comments FROM consultation_feedback WHERE feedback_score < 3 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM consultation_metrics WHERE consultation_type LIKE '%Workshop%' ORDER BY performance_rating DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT analysis_type, COUNT(analysis_id) AS num_analyses FROM consultation_analysis GROUP BY analysis_type HAVING num_analyses > 1 ORDER BY num_analyses DESC;
